narratives.question_text: How would you summarize ECON 110 05 for a fellow student? Would you recommend ECON 110 05 to another student? Why or why not?
comments: WAYYY too much work for a language class. Super hard. Struggling to get above a C. occasionally interesting
I love the Spanish language and would recommend it to everyone who needs language requirements.
A good amount of busy work in the workbook activities and everyday can get a bit tedious, but not too bad.
Professor Sabe is great! There was a lot more work than in L1, but they are often very interesting materials and the professor tries to make the class fun and enjoyable.
Good continuation of elementary Spanish. If you want to learn this is the way to go
Would recommend it because you have to take a language and spanish is very organized.
